Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you guys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Franky asked us to bring you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dream ship has been completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They built an incredible ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's already done?!\NThat was really quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five top-notch shipwrights\Nworked on it day and night!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they did!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's head there right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys running that\Nfrantically for? You're out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, we came\Nto ask you a huge favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the wanted posters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted posters?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, the bounty on\Nyour head has gotten crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all the others, too, are wanted in addition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too?! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of having me explain,\Njust take a look at these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All seven of you now have\Nbounties on your heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy, 300-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It went up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Hunter Zoro, 120-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:04:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat Burglar Nami, 16-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cotton Candy Lover Chopper,\Nthe gang's pet, 50-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil's Child Nico Robin,\N80-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot Sanji, failed to obtained\Na picture, 77-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sogeking's got a bounty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, we sympathize with you, or, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you wanna say all sorts\Nof things, but, well... please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The favor we're talking about\Nhas something to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyborg Franky, 44-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Bro's got a bounty on his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We somehow\Nwere able to get off the hook,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Bro had no such luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he stays in Water Seven,\Nhis life will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets caught again, we're not\Nstrong enough to rescue him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he probably will try to stay on this\Nisland because he's worried about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we got together and discussed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, please! You can\Ndo it by force if you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take Bro out to sea.\NHe's a pirate's son to start with!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how we all feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please consider it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys didn't have to ask me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided a long time ago that he's the\Nonly person I'd accept as our shipwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you guys all okay with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who's this...?\N--I-I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you have your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we know how they feel,\Nwe'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you guys going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scrap heap island is this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... but we're not going to see him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing him would make it\Nhard for us to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mozu! Kiwi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him that we wish him all the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The King of Animals that Overlooks the Sea!\NThe Dream Ship Magnificently Completed!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are prepared for the\Nworst regarding Usopp, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hey, you guys! Just how\Nlong do you have to feel down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Why does mine have to\Nbe the only one that's a drawing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People don't usually start off\Nwith a bounty that large.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Just how does this\Npicture look like me?! Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How could they think this is me?!\N--You look like that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use real words. I don't\Nunderstand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the laughing stock... of all\Nthe ladies throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was tricked...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was a reporter from\None of the local magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least he did manage to\Nget a cute pic of me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally gotten a bounty myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pirate, too! I fought hard like a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna file a complaint\Nabout my 50-Berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's always next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry. Bro's waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna get the ship\Nand Franky and set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, Sanji isn't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave Twirly-brows be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you pirate ladies and guys already leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney, Gonbe, thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is indeed an incredibly rare case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Few though they may be,\Nto think that they all have a bounty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, their bounties\Ntotal over 600 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, this "Black Foot" guy...\Nwhy isn't there any picture of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, well... I am certain\Nthat I took his picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was shocked when I\Nsaw the developed picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is indeed something\Nright out of a horror story!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you take off... the lens cover?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! There's something huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We're here, Franky! Give us the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ice pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, he had to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the ship is completed.\NI'll show it to you in place of Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw its blueprints,\Nmy eyes opened wide in surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can sail any kind of sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this ship, going to the end\Nof the world isn't a mere dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and show it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is Franky's message to you, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to be\NKing of the Pirates someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...board this King of Animals ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What a spectacle!\N--Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! It's huge! It's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it has all sorts of things flying out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He's gonna give this to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... This is at least twice as big as Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a big fore-and-aft sail! Is this a sloop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see the kitchen! The kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fine ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of\Nflower the figurehead is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well, I think it's, of course, the mane of a lion.\N--Whoa! The interior is incredible, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a deck with a lawn! It feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A slide! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we can do gardening, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good view it has!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's the kitchen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That big gaffsail seems\Nto have a lot of mobility!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called brigantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sloop boats sail as people's\Nimagination dictates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The navigator's skills\Ndetermine the sail's usefulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hardly wait! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go check out the ship, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! My dream fridge! One with a\Nlock on it! There's a huge oven, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Franky! This ship is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ice pops. Where's Franky?\NWe'd like to say thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he has no intention\Nof seeing you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to ask him to\Njoin you guys as a shipwright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that he's our shipwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to have realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he doesn't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not sure if he can turn you\Ndown if you ask him face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he went and hid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, his honest wish is...\NHe wants to set sail with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he's entrusting this dream ship that\Nhe's been planning all this time to you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is proof enough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! There's an aquarium here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're right! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky has come to genuinely like you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's imposing a duty upon himself\Nto stay on this island forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a stupid persistence, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really intend to take him with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way to free him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By force?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys said the same thing,\Ntoo, but is that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the start of Bro's new life.\NWe mustn't show tears. Smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... they're coming down\Non their own. What can I... Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! What are you doing back here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why do I need a reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Franky House! It's my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna come right out and say it, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go with the Straw Hats, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I would, is there...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! With your skills, you guys\Ncan't even properly build a single house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just went to see them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to ask them to take you out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools! Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But he had already made up his mind\Nto ask you to be their shipwright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to become a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't take a genius to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had never seen you building a ship before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:14:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought, "Wow, I never\Nknew he could look this happy."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen you having\Nthat much fun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the Straw Hats are looking\Nfor a shipwright, don't you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ran away on purpose, didn't you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wanted poster!\NSo they put it out, as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't stay with us any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wanna be a hindrance to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wanted poster!\NSo they put it out, as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't stay with us any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wanna be a hindrance to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk so cocky! The hell with the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took you all in when you were about\Nto die like dogs on the backstreets!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can't even live\Nwithout me, and... Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got his swimsuit off of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swimsuit? Why'd you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wait! I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good job!\N--Pass it around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it back to him, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my swimsuit back! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my best swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better know that you can't defeat me,\Neven if you all gang up on me at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one survivor would do!\NDeliver his swimsuit to Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:16:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it to the scrap heap island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my swimsuit back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I don't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I saw you had it! Enough of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brother! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! A fake-out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run to the southeast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's this fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The perv is... Franky is going on a rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! He's not wearing anything down below!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Ding-don...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the children inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them see the perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're committing indecent exposure!\NYou're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Deliver... Deliver the swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go ahead of him by Yagara and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The backstreets... have become a battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! My legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Pass it to me! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:19:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Package receipt confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you like the ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen such an incredible ship! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You perv! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Have some shame!\N--You perverted bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is! In addition to my super design,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything you guys requested was added!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the soldier\Ndock system I invented yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the biggest showpiece! I bet you'll like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the fish tank?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put the fish you catch in the fish tank,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can view and enjoy them\Nthrough the big tank downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a room that's like an aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have meals there with the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can always have fresh fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ship is the ultimate dream ship\Nto you guys as well as to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my swimsuit back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's coming! Roronoa-san!\NSanji-san! We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim at the scrap heap island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky Family's specialty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything Cannon! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you guys! Enough with your jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He's flying there before\Nhis swimsuit even gets there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on to me, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that some sort of a curse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! It's just a perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We can see everything!\NWe can see everything!\N--B-Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can see everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best ship ever!\NWe'll take good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I wish you a safe journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.02,0:22:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to give\Nthis swimsuit back to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those idiots... They know they\Ncan't do anything without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cocky of them to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, this town is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys all are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.81,0:22:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Goodbye My Dear Underlings!\NFranky Departs!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.27,0:22:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
